{"tid":847576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國財政部宣布制裁日本黑道山口組","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T09:47:11.000Z","uid":38533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"641d6aca0d3884e6eaca16b87bcd71643292d065","tid":847576,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"美國日前宣佈最新制裁對象，這次矛頭指向日本黑道組織山口組 （Yamaguchi-gumi）。美國財政部表示，已針對兩間與山口組有聯繫的日本公司及四名涉黑人士實施制裁，凍結其由美國管轄的資產，並禁止美國企業與他們有經貿來往，從而打擊跨國犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財政部在聲明表示，此次遭到制裁的房地產公司為「山輝株式會社（Yamaki K.K）」和「東洋信用實業株式會社（Toyo Shinyo Jitsugyo）」，均為山口組的附屬公司。前者擁有山口組神戶總部所在的地皮，後者則負責管理山口組的總部，兩公司都參與房地產商業活動，以及藝術品銷售和高爾夫練習場的管理等業務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.litenews.hk/?p=59866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2F%3Fp%3D59866&d=8BteI%2Bf9ky9hy%2B9tl%2BrAfVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=478bc5f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.litenews.hk/?p=59866</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有咩係美國制裁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6771e96d8ae7fbc40dc7d0ad6fdebc859b871e26","tid":847576,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"左膠"},{"pid":"a05357cb9935144af285cfc0ab4897d3e335766d","tid":847576,"uid":135313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb863e911c97d153fdd38941c79894e402db809","tid":847576,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"幾制裁支那共產黨"},{"pid":"1a385ce87f2dd41e50e5ab32744611f618d815c3","tid":847576,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時制裁支那共產黨</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0c5e1feffed196a143d8e5168eab80e50918dd4"